_sText:
Details:
Well, here is my remake of Halo 2's Zanzibar. After sitting on this map for months trying to fix the problems with it, i have given up lol. Since so many ppl kept spamming me with requests to finish it (you know who you are), i decided to just release it as is and be done with it. i may recompile it in the future, so feel free to make suggestions here. Known problems: 1 Bad CT spawn, very open and somewhat empty, shadow issues on 3 prob_dynamics, dead water, a few black textures, 1 compile glitch (stairs, t spawn) Specs:
40 spawns, working turrets, spawned weapons and grenades scattered around the map, hidden specialty weapons, buyzones.
Please visit Clan 5k3's studio for more Halo css maps and materials.
